overview: Hey, America! Give it up for Danish dazzler, Miss Katja Kean. As you can see, our Katja's a real sport, and she's up for anything from fast foursomes on the back nine to a few rounds on the canvas. Her keen sense of fair play & sportsmanship make her a joy to work up a good, hot sweat with!
title: KKSS: Katja Kean's Sports Spectacular
